 ============
 = Overview =
 ============
A series of generators for common WP tasks, eg. theme and plugin development

 ================
 = INSTRUCTIONS =
 ================

THEMES:
generate.php theme [name] [domain] [dest]

THEME FLAGS:
name: all lower case, dashes between words. my-awesome-theme will become "My Awesome Theme" in style.css
domain: domain.com, www.domain.com, blog.domain.com, etc. No http://
destination: the path to where you want the theme to be created

THEME EXAMPLE:
php path/to/generate.php theme my-awesome-theme mydomain.com /path/to/destination/

************************************

